Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.83,0:00:04.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.30,0:00:05.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Comment: 0,0:00:06.57,0:00:06.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.45,0:00:06.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:08.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:11.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I spent the night here last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.16,0:00:13.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Breakfast is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.35,0:00:15.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:18.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you bring all this from your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.46,0:00:19.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.65,0:00:23.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're more suited to travel than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.87,0:00:25.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.87,0:00:28.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:29.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:32.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried about you since you didn't come yesterday.
Comment: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:33.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,About you, uncessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.48,0:00:35.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really glad I made that wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.06,0:00:36.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.10,0:00:37.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:41.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wished upon the stardust that you would come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.03,0:00:42.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.54,0:00:45.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's have breakfast, breakfast!
Comment: 0,0:00:43.67,0:00:45.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Awkward double breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.43,0:00:45.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:47.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna eat too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.43,0:00:48.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't be such a pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.94,0:00:49.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:51.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so stingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.27,0:00:51.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not stingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.90,0:02:24.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you wait for me this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:26.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.61,0:02:28.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm, I had something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:30.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:31.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.85,0:02:37.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still having those dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.45,0:02:38.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.57,0:02:42.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, it was about a forest at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.58,0:02:44.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was talking with someone in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:45.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:45.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.51,0:02:49.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but there was someone beside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:52.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked her what an ocean was.
Comment: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:54.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gender: He or she?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:57.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, she told me many things about the ocean.
Comment: 0,0:02:57.97,0:02:57.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: many things -> lots
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.81,0:03:00.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was really fun just talking to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:05.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so fun that I wanted to wrap her words up and keep them forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:08.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was that fun, then sleep forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:09.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gao...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.47,0:03:11.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:15.71,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs54\c&HB83D41&\pos(643,96)}Episode 6
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:19.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A fan, a fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:20.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.90,0:03:23.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:24.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:24.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.09,0:03:26.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:29.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How did your puppet shows go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.76,0:03:32.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Well... Not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:33.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:35.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito Kunisaki, you good-for-nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:39.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:40.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:42.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who eats for free shouldn't talk so conceitedly!
Comment: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:42.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Awkward phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.89,0:03:43.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.25,0:03:46.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Playing, eating and sleeping...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.79,0:03:48.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's in a really enviable position.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:52.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, I dreamt of my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.68,0:03:54.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.05,0:03:59.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, we would often sit here together and watch the night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:01.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a dream of those times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:02.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:09.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In each and every star, there is a god watching over us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.19,0:04:13.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They also purify the hearts of those who watch the stars.
Comment: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:15.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: hearts -> souls
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.72,0:04:19.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A short time after that, he left home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:25.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After my younger sister died, my parents started to fight.
Comment: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:25.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: fight -> quarrel
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:27.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:32.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He married another woman in a faraway town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:38.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When he left, he gave me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:43.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you have to work now?
Comment: 0,0:04:43.18,0:04:43.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: + go to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:43.80,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:44.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:48.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Minagi has run away from home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.32,0:04:49.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:50.54,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikako.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:53.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you try to hide it from me, I can tell, because I'm her best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.95,0:04:56.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Things can't remain like this after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.34,0:05:00.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi has to wake up from her dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:02.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.95,0:05:04.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go home now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.37,0:05:05.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:06.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.46,0:05:08.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko pika.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:11.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:12.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:14.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:15.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:21.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry to have bothered you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:22.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:25.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you need anything, don't hesitate to stop by.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:25.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:33.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's starting to remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:34.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:37.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she lost something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.55,0:05:39.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She came here just because of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:44.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just told her that she would eventually remember when she found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:47.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is up to Minagi-san's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:02.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:05.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:08.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to leave town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:09.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:11.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've stayed too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:13.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's time for me to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.99,0:06:16.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I... see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.05,0:06:19.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come with me, Tohno?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:20.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:24.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to show you the world;
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:27.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the real world, not a dream world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:28.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The world...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:32.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go together to discover that world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:39.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:40.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:45.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:47.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:49.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we go,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.79,0:06:52.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to say something to Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.65,0:06:53.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry; just follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:11.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we're finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.32,0:07:16.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:21.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru said that she doesn't want to see Minagi looking sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:22.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:26.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You must decide for yourself what you are going to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.93,0:07:29.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want, you really can come on a journey with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.37,0:07:32.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you along to wherever I end up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:35.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your choice.
Comment: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:35.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: The choice is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:38.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You, Minagi Tohno, must decide of your own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.20,0:08:04.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:16.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy?
Comment: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:17.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother or mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:18.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:52.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.61,0:09:03.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Comment: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:17.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother or mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:17.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The stars are amazing tonight too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.44,0:09:18.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:20.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think Minagi is looking at the stars too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.63,0:09:22.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, probably with her mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:29.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:31.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's getting late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:33.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want, I'll walk you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.15,0:09:38.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:41.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a home to return to.
Comment: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:42.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: I have a place to go back to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:42.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:47.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the sky, there's a really sad-looking girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:48.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:49.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.70,0:09:55.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl always just sees sad dreams and has nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:58.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She can't be happy, so all she can have is sad dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.77,0:10:03.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On her back, she has wounded feathers,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:05.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,feathers with a really mysterious power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:10.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're packed with the memories of many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.16,0:10:15.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked for one of the plumes,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.52,0:10:19.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because there was someone I wanted to comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:26.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I thought if that person became happy, then the girl in the sky would become happy too.
Comment: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:26.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe a split?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.79,0:10:27.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.41,0:10:31.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,People can't live without memories, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.72,0:10:36.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, they can't live on memories alone either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:39.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to wake from your dreams sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:44.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because dreams that you don't wake up from eventually become sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:49.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to return the feather.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.47,0:10:51.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to say goodbye to everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.59,0:10:54.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,'I dont want to say' or 'it's sad to say'
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.59,0:10:54.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but because I'm just a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.18,0:10:58.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because stars must disappear when the sun rises...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.75,0:11:00.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.82,0:11:02.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a fragment of a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:05.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My being here is just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:08.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you know, it was a really fun dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:11.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:12.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:14.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The real Michiru...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:20.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,wasn't allowed to be born into this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:41.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I met Michiru for the first time at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.54,0:11:47.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every day, I went to the station to pick my father up, even after he had left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.34,0:11:52.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Father had already quit his job there,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.55,0:11:55.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but there was nothing else I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.81,0:12:00.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it then that your mother started calling you Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:01.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:07.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But as long as I was Michiru, Mother kept smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:12.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hijiri told me it was around then that you stopped smiling as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:12.35,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:20.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was one summer afternoon after a rain storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:34.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I felt like I had seen her before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:36.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I felt that she was always nearby.
Comment: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:39.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Should a "No" go here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:45.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.48,0:12:47.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:50.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... Minagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.47,0:12:56.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything started with my sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.77,0:12:57.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.02,0:13:04.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't wished for a little sister, no one would have had to dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:11.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I might even have to hurt Michiru,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.80,0:13:16.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but even then, I still want her to meet someone, someone very important.
Comment: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:17.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Koi's: I want to let someone very important catch at least one glimpse of her... this seems clumsy, but I'll let you decide. Also listen to the jap phrasing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:19.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:22.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kei-chan, hurry up, or we won't be able to get a spot at the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.88,0:13:25.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.96,0:13:29.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I fell asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.15,0:13:32.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were probably tried from playing all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:35.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:39.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we have dinner at my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:42.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At Minagi's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:55.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rare for my daughter to bring friends home, so I made a special dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:00.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:04.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't asked you your name yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:05.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:07.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, your name. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:09.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell me your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:13.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.69,0:14:14.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Comment: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:15.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:16.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:19.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:23.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is... Michiru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:26.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.87,0:14:28.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:35.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so your name is Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.05,0:14:39.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:42.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually, really, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:47.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.89,0:14:49.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:50.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.19,0:14:53.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a wonderful name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.43,0:14:54.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:58.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter has always loved hamburgers ever since she was little too.
Comment: 0,0:14:59.43,0:14:59.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: more literally 'my daughter' -> 'this girl' but this might be confusing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.28,0:15:05.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She always said that when she got a little sister, she wanted her to eat my hamburgers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:06.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Minagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.99,0:15:07.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.16,0:15:09.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Michiru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.53,0:15:11.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat the hamburgers before they get cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.50,0:15:14.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You love them too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:15.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.98,0:15:17.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.30,0:15:23.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, are they good?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:25.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they're really delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:28.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,These hamburgers are my own recipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:30.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Comment: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:33.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shorter for timing, just 'here'
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:33.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I taught Minagi how to make them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:34.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:34.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:39.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll make me very happy if you eat lots.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:42.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.38,0:15:57.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:15:59.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:09.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll hold on to this for you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:12.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take good care of it, okay, Minagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.30,0:16:13.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:21.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:23.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:24.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:27.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. She didn't even say goodbye.
Comment: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:27.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: 'without even saying goodbye'
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:27.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:29.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There should still be time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:32.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because the stars aren't out yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:34.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru is probably over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:37.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.05,0:16:38.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:39.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:47.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru, it's not safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:50.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dangerous there, so come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.87,0:16:52.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:54.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.71,0:16:59.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had so much fun, so I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:03.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make a face like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:06.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi, you have to keep smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.74,0:17:08.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I'll be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.47,0:17:10.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:14.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to be myself thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.48,0:17:19.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you leave, I think I won't ever be able to laugh again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:20.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:25.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi, you can laugh with people other than me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:27.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Minagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:29.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito Kunisaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:31.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,let's make a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:32.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:37.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl with wings continues to have sad dreams in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.54,0:17:41.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go back to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:47.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the fun memories you guys gave me back to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:48.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:54.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you find her, I want you to tell her many more happy stories,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.31,0:17:58.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and free her from her sad dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:17:59.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:03.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi, always keep smiling, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:06.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say bye-bye with a smile, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:09.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.18,0:18:13.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say goodbye with a smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:14.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:17.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...because I won't be able to see you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:19.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.95,0:18:22.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because even after you wake up from a dream, the memories will still be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.73,0:18:24.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.42,0:18:29.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Make your memories of me be happy ones, forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.85,0:18:32.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is something only you can do.
Comment: 0,0:18:33.06,0:18:34.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: Only you can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.18,0:18:34.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.07,0:18:35.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:36.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.59,0:18:41.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you smiling now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:42.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:43.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:44.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.75,0:18:47.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then keep smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.57,0:18:49.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say bye-bye with a smile for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.18,0:18:51.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you smiling, Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.95,0:18:52.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:54.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sad to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.84,0:18:56.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:58.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm smiling, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:04.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be wonderful if everyone kept smiling all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.07,0:19:07.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The world would be filled with smiles, and everybody would be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:09.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:12.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.10,0:19:14.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:15.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:29.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:43.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:45.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope you're not running away again.
Comment: 0,0:19:57.59,0:19:57.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,blah not done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:48.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a rice coupon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.65,0:19:52.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a letter from my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:56.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He is inviting me to come see him during the summer holidays.
Comment: 0,0:19:56.99,0:19:57.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,American check: Vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:20:00.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To my surprise, it seems that I have a little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.27,0:20:05.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He and his current wife had a baby girl.
Comment: 0,0:20:05.96,0:20:06.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop current?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:07.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl... Her name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:14.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I was a little hesitant,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.84,0:20:17.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I've decided to go meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:19.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother encouraged me to go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.23,0:20:20.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.04,0:20:22.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohno!
Comment: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:25.75,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuma Recycling
Comment: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:26.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably not bother imo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:28.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wings that cannot fly have a use too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.78,0:20:32.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're precious memories of when you once flew in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.41,0:20:40.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isn't that right, Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:55.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You like bubbles?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.52,0:20:55.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:20:56.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:21:00.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, but, I can't blow them very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.33,0:21:03.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then shall I teach you how to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:04.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.50,0:21:04.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:06.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.15,0:21:09.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Minagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.05,0:21:11.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.13,0:21:13.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's, it's...
Comment: 0,0:21:14.77,0:21:31.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Koi says 'Um... um...' but that doesn't make sense to me. Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.44,0:21:32.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.67,0:21:34.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:36.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
