Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.92,0:23:42.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.92,0:23:46.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a coincidence that I started having dreams, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.38,0:23:50.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt that this summer was special.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.73,0:23:52.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to try my best to make a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.25,0:23:56.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I met you and started having those dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.69,0:23:58.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably all connected, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.76,0:24:01.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I want to do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.00,0:24:04.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make this summer the happiest ever,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.17,0:24:07.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because it's the summer that I met you, Yukito-san.
